  <h2><a href='https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=at.weblogic.ebilly&hl=en'>EBilly</a></h2>
  <h3>EBilly - validate your receipts</h3>
  <p>A new Austrian regulation in 2016 obliged all shops in Austria to digitally sign their receipts.
  The signature is, in most cases, encoded as QRCode and printed on the receipt. Customers have no way of verifying the signature.
  EBilly uses publicly available data from the registered certificate authorities and company registers to cryptographically verify the receipt data,
    and collects the company information.
  </p>

