    <h2><a href='https://github.com/areiter/libecterm'>libecterm</a></h2>
    <h3>Library to comunicate with credit card terminals</h3>
    <p>Libecterm is a .net library implementing the ZVT protocol to communicate with credit card terminals.
      The ZVT protocol is used by major payment companies in Europe for the comunication of credit-card terminals with point-of-sale systems.</p>
    <p>The commercial version of this library has extended command support and also includes support for other terminals not supporting the ZVT protocol</p>

